if (task) {
  tasks.push(task);
  input.value = "";
  input.focus();
  renderTasks();
}


Line	Meaning
if (task)	Only run if user typed something
tasks.push(task)	Add the new task to the array (data update)
input.value = ""	Clear the input box
input.focus()	Put cursor back in the input
renderTasks()	Update the UI to show the new task
